  "content": "<p data-pid=\"AUvZFgq7\">解释概念有两种办法，<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//learning.subwiki.org/wiki/Examples_first\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">例子先行</a>，以及<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//learning.subwiki.org/wiki/Define_then_discuss\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">定义并讨论</a>。但另一条原则是「定义压轴」，我是从这条关于 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/index.php%3Ftitle%3D3blue1brown%26action%3Dedit%26redlink%3D1\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">3blue1brown</a> 的<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3DojjzXyQCzso\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">视频</a>中总结出来的。</p><h3>链接到本文</h3><ul><li data-pid=\"OURbpopN\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/wiki/What_makes_a_word_explanation_good%253F\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">好的文字解释有什么特点？</a><sup data-text=\"好的文字解释有什么特点？\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/602457764\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>  (<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/index.php%3Ftitle%3DSpecial%3AWhatLinksHere%26target%3DWhat%2Bmakes%2Ba%2Bword%2Bexplanation%2Bgood%253F\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">←链接</a>）</li></ul><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"GEc9r4sv\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>感谢主要译者<span class=\"nolink\">S</span>hom、校对 Jarrett Ye<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/wiki/Definitions_last\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Defini